@startuml
actor Admin as "Administrador"
participant UI as "Interfaz"
participant View as "Vista de QR"
participant QR as "Módulo QR"
participant DB as "Base de datos"

Admin -> UI: Solicita generar QR
UI -> View: POST generar QR
View -> QR: generar()
QR -> DB: Crear registro QR
DB --> QR: Código generado
QR --> View: QR creado
View --> Admin: Muestra QR

Admin -> UI: Solicita renovar QR
UI -> View: POST renovar QR
View -> QR: renovar()
QR -> DB: Actualizar fecha de expiración
DB --> QR: QR renovado
QR --> View: Confirmación
@enduml
